high_descs: walk into the drawer bedroom
walk to the butterknife and open the drawer.
pick up a knife from inside the bread drawer
walk with the bread knife to an empty box in the hallway
walk back with the knife to the coffeetable and put down the knife.
walk out of butterknife into the hallway
walk back to the bread in the hallway
pick up a slice of bread from the box
take slice of bread to the microwave
Start the microwave, then open the microwave again take out the slice of bread.
take slice of bread and walk to the fridge
Put the bread in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Get the bread slice to the fridge.

high_descs: Turn left to reach the passage and turn right to head to the bedroom on the right to face the drawer.
Pick up a butterknife from the bottom shelf of the dresser.
Head to the bread on the left and turn right to head down the passage and reach the box.
Cut the bread in the box into slices with the knife.
Turn around to head down the passage and turn right to reach the round coffeetable.
Put the butterknife on the coffeetable.
Turn around to head out the room and turn left to head down the passage to reach the bread box.
Pick up the slice of the bread from the box.
Turn around to head down the passage and head to the kitchen on the right to reach the microwave.
Heat the bread in the microwave and take it out.
Turn left to reach the fridge.
Put the bread in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put the heated slice of Bread in the Fridge.

high_descs: Turn left and go straight until reaching the hallway, then turn right and take the first right from there into the bedroom, approaching the drawers to the left.
Remove the butterknife from the drawers.
Exit the room the way you came in, turn right and head straight down the hall to the end, stopping at the bread on the floor.
Cut the bread inside the box.
Turn around and go down the hall, entering the second door on the right, approaching the circular white coffeetable.
Place the butterknife down on the coffeetable.
Return to the box with the sliced bread.
Pick up a slice of bread.
Turn around and go straight down the hall until reaching the kitchen area on the left, and go towards the microwave on the corner of the counters.
Use the microwave on the bread.
Go towards the fridge to your left in this same area.
Place the bread in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Place a microwaved slice of Bread in a Fridge.
